Text:
As far as I can tell the audio is all good quality compared to some.  I had to download 42 from another source and that is not quite as good but not terrible.

Also, the transcript has episode 18 and 19 mixed up.  Notice the the date for 19 is May 11th and the date for 18 is May 12th.

Other than that everthing should be in order.

Please comment on any other issues you may find and seed as long as you can.

Enjoy!!!
